[Kingdom_Hearts_II|Kingdom Hearts II]]|developer=Square Enix|publisher=Square Enix U.S.A., Buena Vista Games |date=2006-03-28 |platform=PlayStation 2 }}</ref>。當他對上了克勞德時且突然消失了，索拉認為他們到別的地方繼續他們的戰鬥<ref>'''Goofy:''' Where'd they go? Do ya think they made it back to their own world? / '''Sora:''' They went somewhere else... Cloud went to fight a great battle--to defeat the darkness inside him. {{cite video game|title=[[Kingdom_Hearts_II|Kingdom Hearts II]]|developer=Square Enix|publisher=Square Enix U.S.A., Buena Vista Games |date=2006-03-28 |platform=PlayStation 2 }}</ref>。野村表示，賽菲羅斯在遊戲中代表了克勞德黑暗的一面，相較之下蒂法則代表了他的光明面<ref>{{cite book |title=Kingdom Hearts: Chain of Memories Ultimania |year=2005|isbn=978-4-7575-1621-2 |language=ja | publisher=Square-Enix |pages=}}</ref>。雖然賽菲羅斯沒有出現在前傳《[[王國之心_夢中降生|王國之心 夢中降生]]》，但當中的[[札克斯·菲爾|札克斯·菲爾]]卻立志要成為英雄。工作人員這樣表示，但不知道他們是否會將他描繪成一個黑暗般的幸福<ref name="bbs">{{cite book |title=キングダム ハーツ バース バイ スリープ アルティマニア|year=2010 |isbn=978-4-7575-2788-1 |language=ja | publisher=Square-Enix |pages=}}</ref>。賽菲羅斯的第四個亮相是《[[富豪街|富豪街]]》，在當中他作為是可解開使用的人物<ref>{{cite video game |publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] |developer=[[Paon|Paon]] |title=[[Itadaki_Street#Dragon_Quest_&_Final_Fantasy_in_Itadaki_Street_Special|Itadaki Street Special]] |platform=PlayStation 2 |date=2004-12-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite video game |title=[[Itadaki_Street#Dragon_Quest_&_Final_Fantasy_in_Itadaki_Street_Portable|Itadaki Street Portable]] |developer=[[Paon|Paon]] |publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] |date=2006-05-26 |platform=[[PlayStation_Portable|PlayStation Portable]]}}</ref>。

